result.name: newcastle-city-council-cycle-parking-in-the-urban-core
result.notes:
Locations of cycle parking in the Urban Core with details on the number of spaces, type of stand, the main land use attractor, if it is covered and its condition. This data covers publicly available cycle parking in Newcastle-upon-Tyne's Urban Core. Its intended use is to illustrate the approximate location of cycle parking and how many spaces are available at that location

Data captured using handheld GPS unit and OS 1:10,000 Raster files. Data was captured in October 2015 and is expected to be updated bi-annually
result.title: Cycle Parking in the Urban Core
